chapters.title: You will need a 6x base platform
Place pressure plates, stone, stone bricks, sticku pistons and water
Step Place glass, stone, redstone, repeaters and redstone torch
Step B Place glass, stone, ladders and redstone torch
Place glass, stone slabs, stone, stone bricks and sticky pistons
Place glass, stone, obsidian, redstone and redstone torch
Build mob tube to mob spanner (20 blocks)
You will need to hook this wire upto a lever to control the mob platforms
